          <p class="muted">The 2017 Tax Cuts and Jobs Act changed corporate tax rates and individual brackets and is widely cited by supporters as a pro-growth reform. Read an official summary for businesses and CRS analysis for details.</p>
          <p class="sources">Sources: IRS summary; Congressional Research Service. :contentReference[oaicite:5]{index=5}</p>
